If the system of equations involving \( x \) and \( y \)

\[
\left\{
\begin{array}{l}
\sin x = m \sin^3 y, \\
\cos x = m \cos^3 y
\end{array}
\right.
\]

has real solutions, then what is the range of positive values for \( m \)?

